"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/af9bd30e8dd89c5bdc42d67ff5595cb5/e3f56/note.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af9bd30e8dd89c5bdc42d67ff5595cb5/e3f56/note.png 22w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 22px) 100vw, 22px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    注意事项</h3>\n<p>若勾选了“只处理选中对象”，则聚类后只会生成面数据集，不会在源数据集中增加分类字段。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"点密度聚类","next":null,"prev":null},"fields":{"path":"content\\tutorial\\DataProcessing\\Vector\\AggregatePoints.zh.md","slug":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Vector/AggregatePoints/","langKey":"zh"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/zh/tutorial/DataProcessing/Vector/AggregatePoints/"}}}